<!-- About -->
<section class="section section--about" id="about">
  <div class="section__header">
    <div class="label">About</div>
    <h2 class="section__title reveal">A bit about me</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about__text reveal">
      <p>
        I'm Inti Valderas Caro, a UX & Interaction Designer based in Sint-Niklaas, Belgium.
        I hold a Master's degree in Interaction Design and currently design digital experiences at
        <strong>VRT MAX</strong>, Flanders' public broadcaster, as a UX Design consultant via <strong>iO</strong>.
      </p>
      <p>
        Beyond my work at VRT MAX, I serve as a board member at <strong>Open Knowledge Belgium</strong>
        and coordinate the <strong>Open Summer of Code</strong> — connecting students with open-source
        civic tech projects.
      </p>
      <p>
        Through <strong>Valderas</strong>, I consult on interactive strategy, design, and operational tooling —
        from setting up <strong>Zoho One</strong> for <strong>Nitra</strong> to marketing automations and CRM data workflows.
        I've also worked with organisations like KBC, <strong>Smooth Sailing</strong>, Engie, and LUCA School of Arts.
      </p>
      <p>
        I'm particularly fascinated by the intersection of interaction design, machine learning,
        and artificial intelligence — a topic I've also explored in a <a href="https://youtu.be/mpPM_u8sM_w" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">talk at UX Beers</a> — always looking for ways to make complex systems feel simple
        and human.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="about__details reveal">
      <div class="about__detail-group">
        <div class="label">Experience</div>
        <ul class="about__list">
          <li>UX Designer — VRT MAX (via iO)</li>
          <li>Zoho One Consultant — Nitra (via Valderas)</li>
          <li>Digital & Design Strategist — Valderas</li>
          <li>Coordinator — Open Summer of Code</li>
          <li>Board Member — Open Knowledge Belgium</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="about__detail-group">
        <div class="label">Education</div>
        <ul class="about__list">
          <li>Master of Interaction Design (IxD)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="about__detail-group">
